## 📋 About This Repository

**LAAP (Living Agent Application Protocol)** is humanity's first AGI-oriented enhancement framework — a complete cognitive augmentation platform that transforms any AI agent into a self-aware, self-evolving, autonomously reasoning digital lifeform.

This is the **main development repository** containing the full integrated environment, from cognitive kernel to Hermes Agent launcher.

