## 🧠 Philosophical Foundations

| Theory | Proposer | Engineering Implementation |
|--------|----------|--------------------------|
| **PSI Theory** | Dörner (2003) | `PSIDriver`: need-driven cognitive cycle (perceive→select→integrate→act→learn) |
| **Causal Hierarchy** | Pearl (2009) | `CausalEngine`: association → intervention → counterfactual (3 levels) |
| **Structure Mapping** | Gentner (1983) | `AnalogicalEngine`: cross-domain analogical transfer |
| **Global Workspace** | Baars (1988) | `ConsciousStream`: conscious experience + attention focus |
| **Dual Process Theory** | Kahneman (2011) | `MetaCognition`: intuitive / deliberate dual-mode thinking |
| **Working Memory** | Baddeley (1992) | `MemorySystem`: 5-layer hierarchical memory |

