## 🚀 Quick Start

```bash
# Full V5.0 mode (all 32 modules)
laap v5
# or
python laap-hermes-v5

# Lightweight bridge
python laap-hermes-v5 --v4-bridge

# Pure Hermes (no cognitive enhancements)
python laap-hermes-v5 --hermes
```

### As standalone Python package

```bash
pip install laap-brain
```

```python
from laap_brain import enhance
brain = enhance()
brain.before_turn("Analyze system performance bottleneck")
```

