## 🔄 Runtime Mode Switching

After launch, use `/laap-mode` to switch between bridge modes:

| Command | Mode | Description |
|---------|------|-------------|
| `/laap-mode v5` | ⭐ V5 Full | PSI + V5 engine (32 classes) |
| `/laap-mode v4-bridge` | V4 Lite | Lightweight PSI kernel |
| `/laap-mode hermes` | H Pure | No cognitive enhancements |
| `/laap-mode agi` | AGI | AGI Bridge (18 modules) |

